{{Quote|How would Yun-Txiin and Yun-Q'aah view the sacrifice of only one twin?''"<br />"''The Twins do not demand sacrifices, but the Balance is all.|[[Nom Anor]] and [[Kol Yabu]]|<ref name="The New Jedi Order: Star by Star">''[[The New Jedi Order: Star by Star]]''</ref>}}
'''Yun-Q'aah''' was a [[Gender/Legends|female]] [[Yuuzhan Vong]] [[Yun'o|deity]] and one half of the [[Lover Gods]], with [[Yun-Txiin]] being the other. Having a relationship outside one's [[Yuuzhan Vong castes|caste]] was forbidden, and disobeying automatically led to sacrifice to the Lover Gods.

